{"body":"### BYOK keys never reach persistence validation

**High Severity**

<!-- DESCRIPTION START -->
`/api/settings` now accepts `gemini_api_key`, `openrouter_api_key`, and `cerebras_api_key`, but those fields are forwarded to `world_logic.update_user_settings_unified` where centralized validation does not recognize them. This causes key-only updates to fail and mixed updates to silently drop API keys while still returning success.
<!-- DESCRIPTION END -->

<!-- BUGBOT_BUG_ID: 89ad5a84-85a7-4de7-9c7e-0f085db608cb -->

