{"body":"### Query bypass branch never runs

**Medium Severity**

<!-- DESCRIPTION START -->
The new query-parameter auth bypass path is effectively unreachable. It still requires `X-Test-Bypass-Auth`, and requests with that header already return in the earlier bypass branch. As a result, `test_user_id` and `test_user_email` from URL params are never applied, so the new “URL parameter-based” flow in `main.py` does not work as intended.
