{"body":"### Pagination skips equal sort-key documents

**Medium Severity**

<!-- DESCRIPTION START -->
`_InMemoryFirestoreQuery.start_after()` compares only ordered field values and treats exact ties as “not after.” With non-unique sort fields like `last_played`, documents sharing the cursor’s value are dropped from later pages. This makes mock-mode pagination diverge from Firestore and can silently miss campaigns.
<!-- DESCRIPTION END -->

