`main.py` adds `_validate_api_key` with different bypass rules than `settings_validation.validate_api_key`. One uses `app.config['TESTING']`, the other uses `TESTING_AUTH_BYPASS`. The same request can be accepted by one layer and rejected by the other, causing inconsistent `/api/settings` behavior.
