{"body":"### BYOK input listeners accumulate on re-entry

**Medium Severity**

<!-- DESCRIPTION START -->
`setupBYOKEventListeners()` is re-invoked during SPA settings initialization, but the `focus`/`blur`/`keydown` handlers on API key inputs are only appended and never removed. Unlike toggle/clear buttons, inputs are not de-duplicated, so repeated visits stack handlers and trigger multiple `saveSettings()` calls per single edit.
<!-- DESCRIPTION END -->

