{"body":"### Mock pagination cursor compares wrong field

**Medium Severity**

<!-- DESCRIPTION START -->
`_InMemoryFirestoreQuery.start_after` converts a document cursor to `doc.id`, but later compares that cursor against `order_by` field values. In `get_campaigns_for_user`, this means a `DocumentSnapshot` cursor is matched against timestamps, so pagination in mock mode can return duplicated or skipped campaigns instead of the next page.
<!-- DESCRIPTION END -->

